{"tid":987640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高中正妹10年挑戰　網驚豔封她「國民初戀」","createTime":"2019-01-19T13:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T13:05:42.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7979b2eeffebe0af185a730edc7f1d018ed07b55","tid":987640,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n最近網路上掀起「十年挑戰」（#10yearschallenge）的熱潮，許多人紛紛跟風PO出自己十年對比的照片，一位越南女學生也分享自己的照片，女大十八變的容貌引起許多當地媒體報導。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/19/1743496-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F19%2F1743496-XXL.jpg&h=9c52e11f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陶燕妮PO出自己的「十年挑戰」。（圖／翻攝自臉書Đ&agrave;o Yến Nhi）<br />\n根據外媒報導，這名女孩叫陶燕妮（Dao Yen Nhi），照片中可以看到她擁有西方混血外型，白皙的皮膚、深邃的五官加上一頭浪漫長髮，清新的模樣讓她被封為「國民初戀」，甚至有網友稱她是「東南亞最佳初戀顏值」，笑稱這夢幻的外表彷彿看見自己的初戀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/19/1743492-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F19%2F1743492-XXL.jpg&h=9f54da60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲清新外表被封為「國民初戀」。（圖／翻攝自臉書Đ&agrave;o Yến Nhi）<br />\n陶燕妮出生於2002年，現在還是一名高中學生，報導稱她擁有法國血統，表示因為自己住在鄉下，小鎮不太發達因此沒有太多條件能拍照，當初只是單純想分享自己的照片，沒想到會引發這麼多人關注，她也希望未來有機會的話能夠擔任服裝模特兒。（實習編輯：黃韻璇）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/19/1743494-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F19%2F1743494-XXL.jpg&h=70697f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陶燕妮擁有法國血統。（圖／翻攝自臉書Đ&agrave;o Yến Nhi）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=487486\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487486&d=LhHcmVfiNK42SI8LqBdBTsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=49a52211\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487486&h=58562346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=487486</a>"},{"pid":"391baa5d93150560827170f2e95e291ba1c56473","tid":987640,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"嘩我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773fd3942af77ca4290c8e0067eac5a4476a3f21","tid":987640,"uid":153497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fdc78d10b4f1e236b45115a6553b70a08faff9","tid":987640,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391baa5d93150560827170f2e95e291ba1c56473","tid":987640,"uid":58140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"嘩我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"你屌我唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ef37082730e5e2da0412843fd94bc06968ab7c","tid":987640,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"乜撚野taste"},{"pid":"55c727ab43bb5ccd002875f015c16114b2e0d985","tid":987640,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289196e8e2c7c84735b40c9d87a6c1c0e50d7dc3","tid":987640,"uid":212317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"雞樣  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj